<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī ḥ§</hi> varaiyeṟṟa ce
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ntamiḻ ci cuntarapāṇṭiya
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṉ vārtulai <unclear>ni</unclear>rttirai ye
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṟṟa tillaiyileṟiya potu
<lb n="5"/>tikiri kirirattaraiyeṟṟa to
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḷavaṉ taṉmuṉpu tāṉ mikattā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḻnta piṉṉumurai yeṟṟam
<lb n="8"/>peṟṟate tirttaṭṭileṟi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ya voṅku poṉṉe U
<lb n="10"/>Ilakaṭivāraṇac cuntarapā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṇṭiyaṉeṟu polantulai
<lb n="12"/>kaṭavāve tirttaṭṭoṉṟu
<lb n="13"/>metoḻuvār maṉattil nilai
<lb n="14"/>kaṭavāvampalavarkku muttampa
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṭu neṭiya Alaikaṭalāṉatum po
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ṉ paṭumāmalaiyāṉatume §
</p>

